Revision history for Perl application App::SourcePlot

1.23 2014-09-12

    - Updated the included JCMT pointing catalog.

1.22 2014-03-05

    - Updated the included JCMT pointing catalog.
    - Bug fix for elevation vs. time plot wrapping around.

1.21 2013-11-29
    - Increase number of grid lines for elevation.

1.20 2013-09-24
    - Assume hours for RJ/RB RA coordinates without colons.

1.19 2013-05-29
    - Updated the included JCMT pointing catalog.
    - New source window opens with blank fields.
    - Bug fix for time as the y-axis.
    - Used Config::IniFiles to handle the configuration file.
    - Removed obsolete code.
    - Added Galactic and Az/El coordinate choices.

1.18 2012-07-09
    - Moved application code to an App/SourcePlot.pm module.

1.17 2012-07-06
    - Updated to use Astro::Coords and Astro::Catalog.

1.15 2004-07-15
    - Updated Tk parameter names for Perl 5.8 and Tk 804.

1.11 1999-10-28
    - Y2K compliant.

1.08 1999-08-12
    - Draw RA-Dec box with Az-El vectors.

1.03 1998-12-11
    - Load settings from the .splotcfg file.

1.00 1998-08-24
    - Initial version.
